==内装与公共艺术==
本站将汽车元素深化为汽车轮毂天花造型，结合灯光装饰，在增加空间活动的同时，体现龙泉汽车文化<ref>{{cite news | title =成都地铁2号线东延线车站亮相 主打龙泉特色 | publisher =成都全搜索 | date =2014-10-09 | url =http://news.chengdu.cn/content/2014-10/09/content_1559060_2.htm | accessdate =2014-10-09 | language =zh | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171209204041/http://news.chengdu.cn/content/2014-10/09/content_1559060_2.htm | archive-date =2017-12-09 | dead-url =yes }}</ref>。

